flowchart TB
  Dev[npm run dev] --> TSX[tsx server/index.ts]
  TSX --> VDev[Vite middleware (dev)<br/>server/vite.ts]
  TSX --> DevRun[Single Node process<br/>serves API + SPA + WS]

  Build[npm run build] --> Script[tsx script/build.ts]
  Script --> VBuild[Vite build (client)<br/>dist/public]
  Script --> ESBuild[esbuild bundle (server)<br/>dist/index.cjs]
  ESBuild --> ProdRun[npm run start<br/>node dist/index.cjs]
  VBuild --> ProdRun
